0. Current node versions: $ nvm ls
1. Install curl: $ sudo apt-get install curl
2. Visit https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm and copy `curl -o- ...`
3. Rerun shell: $ exec bash
4. Test: $ command -v nvm (must output: nvm)
5. Run: $ nvm install 10 (gatsby tip)
6. Run: $ nvm use 10
7. Test: $ node --version
8. Test: $ npm --version
9. Test: $ nvm ls
10.Run: $ nvm alias default 10
11.(optional) Run: $ nvm install 12
12.Verify: $ nvm ls-remote
